summary:
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: Natwag Makeup Remover Pads,18 Pack 3.74 Inch Reusable Microfiber Cleansing Pad with Laundry Bag Suitable for All Skin Types,3 Color Facial Cleansing Pad Set.
Review Date: 2020/08/18
Store: Natwag
Average Rating: 4.6
Product Details: {'Brand': 'Natwag', 'Skin Type': 'All Skin,Dry', 'Material Feature': 'Reusable', 'Unit Count': '18.00 Count', 'Number of Items': '18', 'Package Dimensions': '4.4 x 4.37 x 2.59 inches; 3.84 Ounces', 'UPC': '745103569701'}
Review Text: This took off layers of foundation and contouring easily, but was soft on the skin while removing them. I like the loops on each pad because I can hook a finger through the loop to keep the pad in place while I wash my face.
Review Title: Soft on skin, hard on makeup
Rating: 5.0
--------------------------------------------------
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: Biutee Poly Nail Gel Kit 15ml 0.53oz Pink Nail Extension Gel Builder Gel Long Lasting Nail Salon Nail Art Design DIY at Home Beginner Friendly…
Review Date: 2020/09/09
Store: Biutee
Average Rating: 3.6
Product Details: {'Package Dimensions': '3.5 x 2 x 1.5 inches; 0.81 Ounces'}
Review Text: The polygel is very sticky and hard to smooth out on the mold. I used nail polish remover in between nails to make it a little easier. Once the gel was finally applied, I was impressed, but the nails only lasted two days before falling off during daily activities like washing my hair and doing the dishes. And that was after I put dip powder on top of the polygel for color. Also note that this is only the gel, you have to order a mold separately to help put them on.
Review Title: Not long lasting
Rating: 3.0
--------------------------------------------------
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: 3 Packs Braiding Hair Extensions 165G Jumbo Braiding Hair High Temperature Synthetic Fiber Jumbo Braiding Hair Extensions ( Blue)
Review Date: 2020/09/09
Store: UHair
Average Rating: 4.5
Product Details: {'Brand': 'UHair', 'Material': 'Human Hair', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Material Feature': 'Natural'}
Review Text: I was a little worried because the packaging was ripped when it came. And this is the packaging that within the Amazon package. Luckily all 3 packs were there. I was also worried because the hair looked really plastic-y .Once I started using it though, it was really easy to work with! I ended up cutting the hair to make shorter box braids though because it was so long. I would recommend ordering 2 to cover your whole head. I needed 6 packs to do a full head of box braids.
Review Title: Great for box braids!
Rating: 4.0
--------------------------------------------------
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: 6 Packs/Lot 26 Inch Pre-stretched Braiding Hair Professional Perm Yaki Synthetic Hair Braids(Ombre Brown Blond,#1B/30/27)
Review Date: 2020/10/11
Store: Alishow
Average Rating: 4.7
Product Details: {'Brand': 'Alishow', 'Material': 'Synthetic', 'Extension Length': '26 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Package Dimensions': '16.97 x 12.48 x 2.52 inches; 2.07 Pounds', 'UPC': '727196547491'}
Review Text: This hair does not tangle much at all! It was great for making small box braids. I sealed the ends with boiling water which worked just fine. It took 2 rounds of dipping my hair in the water to seal them though. The hair is separated into bundles and separated with twist ties. I like the twist ties better than bundles that are separated with hair ties. The twist ties were easier to get off without tangling the hair. I used olive oil, edge control, and hair gel infused with castor oil to braid my hair. All of the products worked well with the hair. I would definitely get this again.
Review Title: Great braiding hair!
Rating: 5.0
--------------------------------------------------
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: Senegalese Twist Crochet Braids Wavy Twist Crochet Hair 14 Inch 5 Packs Wavy Ends free Synthetic Hair Extension Curly Crochet Twist Hair (1B#)
Review Date: 2020/12/22
Store: Liang Dian
Average Rating: 4.7
Product Details: {'Brand': 'Liang Dian', 'Material': 'Synthetic', 'Extension Length': '14 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Curly', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Package Dimensions': '8.78 x 8.35 x 2.64 inches; 8.47 Ounces', 'UPC': '738631321149'}
Review Text: I had never crocheted hair in before these, but I had no issues! The hair came with a crochet tool and the loops were wide enough to work with, I only had to expand them a little bit when installing. It took me about 2 hours and all of the packs to do my hair and I love the result! They are much lighter than box braids and very low maintenance. I have gotten a ton of compliments about how they look! The hair also came with some little multi-colored hair jewels to spice up the twists, which was a nice little gift from the vendor!
Review Title: Lightweight and so pretty!
Rating: 5.0
--------------------------------------------------
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: Altaba Long Wavy Wigs Ombre Red Synthetic Wigs Middle Part Natural Looking Heat Resistant Party Cosplay Full Wig for Women
Review Date: 2021/05/01
Store: Altaba
Average Rating: 3.1
Product Details: {'Material': 'Synthetic', 'Hair Type': 'Wavy', 'Style': 'Wavy', 'Special Feature': 'Glueless', 'Brand': 'Altaba'}
Review Text: I love the color and feel of this wig. It is vibrant, flowy, and truly makes me feel gorgeous. However, there is a distinct line across the middle part that I cannot pluck away so there is a clear line at the scalp separating the hair from the forehead. If I could just pluck the wig to have a better hairline, I would rate this higher.
Review Title: Gorgeous color, not a great part
Rating: 3.0
--------------------------------------------------
=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: UJM Magnetic Eyelashes 10 Pairs Reusable Magnetic Eyelash and Eyeliner Kit Natural Look False Lashes with Tweezers No Glue Needed Waterproof Magnetic Lashes
Review Date: 2021/05/11
Store: UJM
Average Rating: 4.2
Product Details: {'Brand': 'UJM', 'Item Dimensions LxWxH': '8 x 4 x 0.4 inches', 'Material Feature': 'Gluten Free', 'Item Form': 'Pair', 'Mounting Type': 'Eyelash Glue', 'Product Dimensions': '8 x 4 x 0.4 inches; 2.89 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'UJM-010'}
Review Text: Okay, so these are not the best for beginners. I am new to makeup and lashes and I struggled HARD with these. The liner is hard to control and leaks a bit. I have had it seep into the corners of my eyes multiple times and it stings a little bit. The eyelashes stick on well everywhere except for the inside of the eyelid. The last magnet often lifts upward right by the tear duct. It is really hard to keep the whole lash down. I have successfully applied them once. Really would not recommend for beginners.
Review Title: Not for begginers
Rating: 3.0
--------------------------------------------------

POSITIVE SUMMARY:
The user has expressed high satisfaction with several products, particularly appreciating their effectiveness and ease of use. They enjoyed the gentle yet efficient formula of a cleansing pad, which effortlessly removes makeup without irritating the skin. In addition, the user found particular hairstyles easy to manage and style, receiving compliments on their appearance with various hair extensions. They also noted the lightweight nature of certain styles, enhancing comfort and minimizing maintenance. The overall positive experiences highlight effective and user-friendly beauty products that align well with their preferences.

NEGATIVE SUMMARY:
The user has encountered frustrations with some products in their shopping history. Specific challenges included difficulties in applying a nail gel due to its stickiness and lack of longevity, as the nails did not endure typical daily activities. Concerns arose from the packaging quality of a hair extension, along with an awkward fit of a wig that showcased a noticeable part that affected its overall appearance. Furthermore, several products proved to be unsuitable for beginners, particularly magnetic eyelashes that were difficult to apply, causing discomfort during use. 

OVERALL SUMMARY:
The user's shopping history reflects a mixed experience across various beauty products. Positive aspects included effective makeup removal and fulfilling hair extension needs, along with compliments received on certain styles. However, challenges arose with products that underperformed, such as less durable nail gels and wigs with unappealing hairlines. Moreover, difficulties in application for beginners, especially with magnetic eyelashes, highlighted areas where products fell short. Overall, the user values effective beauty solutions but has faced significant struggles with product usability and durability.

target_interaction.title: Look nice, bright colors
target_interaction.text: The colors in this kit are super vibrant, almost neon. I love how much they stand out! I have gotten a ton of compliments on them. The picture shows the matte topcoat which I am not sure you can really see well on such bright colors. I am excited about having the topcoat, but for darker colors where the matte would be better contrasted. The gel is not the longest lasting that I've had and I've noticed the matte top coat specifically burns a little on my nails when under UV light. The color will last about a week, though I have had a couple of fingers peel off before that.
